        of <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">years</TIMEX> of work by <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">scientists</ENAMEX> and staggering financial investments by <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">governments</ENAMEX>,
        <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">universities</ENAMEX>, and tax-exempt <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">foundations</ENAMEX>? What uses should the documents' <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">owners</ENAMEX>
