        Access <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Publishing</ENAMEX>.) When a document is ‚Äúfreely available,‚Äù someone who comes across it may
        be permitted to do nothing more than read it online on a <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">publisher</ENAMEX>'s Web site; the right to
